			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				1)goto nomsoe in temple of life and talk to him until you get the blessed oil of estle.<BR>
2) get hay in the crow fields in west karana. the millers drop this, so it might take a while to find<BR>
3) goto feerott. take a right when u enter the zone and follow it to the undead stones. keep following the<BR>
wall past the spectar cave (watch out for spectars) and eventually you will reach the river. Roror is usually there where<BR>
the mountains meet the river. GIve him 66g and the hay and he will charm it. <BR>
4) go back to rivervale. combine oil and the charmed hay in the forge near the druids. YOU DONT NEED ANY SKILL IN<BR>
BLACKSMITHING TO DO THIS. DONT WASTE YOUR POINTS.<BR>
5) it will give u a bag of writhing hay. give this to shakey the scarecrow<BR>
- the item he gives u is random. it is either the belt or the wee harvester. both are good items if<BR>
u are a halfling druid.
				</font>
